<h2>Vascular Study</h2>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/images/services_vascular.jpg" class="img-responsive img-rounded" />
            <div class="div_space20"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <p>Vascular studies are tests that check the blood flow in your arteries and veins. These tests are noninvasive. Vascular studies use high-frequency sound waves (ultrasound) to measure the amount of blood flow in your blood vessels.</p>
            <p>Following are list of vascular exams :</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Abdominal Doppler</li>
                <li>AV Fistula / AV Graft</li>
                <li>Carotid</li>
                <li>Jugular Veins</li>
                <li>Upper / Lower Extremities Arteries and Veins</li>
                <li>Scrotal Doppler</li>
                <li>Pelvis Doppler (Ovaries)</li>
                <li>Re flux Study</li>
                <li>Renal Transplant</li>
                <li>Liver Transplant</li>
                <li>Pancreatic Transplant</li>
                <li>Umbilical Artery</li>
                <li>Placental Artery</li>
                <li>ABI (Ankle Bronchial Index)</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="div_space20"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

